The fluorescence quantum yield of N-GQDs was 88.20 % (Fig. S1), which was much higher than those prepared by other methods (the detailed measurement process see 
                           Electronic Supplementary Information
                        ). Meantime, the lifetime of N-GQDs was 12.29 ns with the emission wavelength in the region of 300 ∼ 600 nm (Fig. S2).
